The paper discusses the performance of genetic algorithms on multimodal functions and proposes a new mutation operator. This falls under the category of optimization and search algorithms, which is covered by several sub-categories in arXiv CS. cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) is the most likely category as it specifically deals with evolutionary algorithms. cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) are also likely categories as they cover optimization algorithms. cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.DM (Discrete Mathematics) are less likely but still possible categories as they may cover aspects of optimization and search algorithms.
